    "description": "<p>SingHealth Polyclinics, a leader in family medicine, provides seamless, patient-centred and preventive healthcare that is affordable and accessible to all.</p>\n\n<p>SingHealth Polyclinics' network of 8 polyclinics provides primary healthcare services to the community. It plays an integral role in promoting a healthy lifestyle within the community and empowering families with the knowledge of common health issues, care and treatment options.<br />\n<br />\nSingHealth Polyclinics is a member of Singapore Health Services (SingHealth) - a public healthcare cluster which also manages two hospitals and five specialty centres.</p>\n",
